snippet.title: Project L Is Now 2XKO
snippet.description:
Viewer Discretion is Advised. A small percentage of people may experience epileptic seizures when exposed to certain visual images, flashing lights or light patterns.

We named the game.

2XKO, formerly known as Project L, is our upcoming 2v2 tag-based fighting game. Follow us here and on our new socials for all future updates.

#2XKO #ProjectL #RiotGames

Find us on:
Facebook: https://facebook.com/play2XKO
Instagram: https://instagram.com/2XKO
X: https://twitter.com/play2XKO
TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@2xko
